page.enlisting:
• “AIR” stands for Aviation Into-plane Reimbursement card • Assigned to aircraft, not individual • Split billing applies • Enables authorized State & Local Agencies to buy & pay for fuel and fuel related services while conducting official counter drug activities, homeland security and 1st Responders duties for their state. The AIR Card® may not be used for any other purpose • The AIR Card® may be used at participating commercial airports and DoD locations (prior approval is necessary to access military bases) •
